Package: kdetoys-dbg
Section: debug
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, kde-runtime-dbg
Suggests: kdetoys
Priority: extra
Description: debugging symbols for kdetoys
 This package contains the debugging symbols associated with kdetoys.
 They will automatically be used by gdb for debugging kdetoys-related
 issues.
